  "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"neonrooks\" data-post=\"3\" data-topic=\"2253\" data-full=\"true\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/n/9de0a6/48.png\" class=\"avatar\"> neonrooks:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>I use the Bitcoin Core gui (bitcoin-qt) exclusively because it is more convenient for me. I\u2019m concerned about one day not being able to update after the gui is depracated. Is there a solution for non-technical users?</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>I think the node could have a web UI like i2p router web console. Not sure about the wallet.</p>\n<details>\n<summary>Archive</summary>\n<aside class=\"onebox discoursetopic\" data-onebox-src=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20260214133933/https://delvingbitcoin.org/t/the-future-of-the-bitcoin-core-gui/2253/5\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n      <img src=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/original/1X/863d31b22a9d4d4072777bffb9b9ded86a1638bc.svg\" class=\"site-icon\" alt=\"\" data-dominant-color=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\">\n\n      <a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20260214133933/https://delvingbitcoin.org/t/the-future-of-the-bitcoin-core-gui/2253/5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\" title=\"01:36PM - 14 February 2026\">Delving Bitcoin \u2013 14 Feb 26</a>\n  </header>\n\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    <img src=\"https://delvingbitcoin.org/uploads/default/original/1X/863d31b22a9d4d4072777bffb9b9ded86a1638bc.svg\" class=\"thumbnail onebox-avatar\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\">\n\n<div class=\"title-wrapper\">\n  <h3><a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20260214133933/https://delvingbitcoin.org/t/the-future-of-the-bitcoin-core-gui/2253/5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">The future of the Bitcoin Core GUI</a></h3>\n  <div class=\"topic-category\">\n      <span class=\"badge-wrapper bullet\">\n        <span class=\"badge-category-bg\" style=\"background-color: #F7941D;\"></span>\n        <span class=\"badge-category clear-badge\">\n          <span class=\"category-name\">Implementation</span>\n        </span>\n      </span>\n    <div class=\"topic-header-extra\">\n      <div class=\"list-tags\">\n        <div class=\"discourse-tags\">\n          <svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-tag svg-icon svg-string\"><use href=\"#tag\"></use></svg>\n            <span class=\"discourse-tag simple\">bitcoin-core</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n  <p>I think the node could have a web UI like i2p router web console. Not sure about the wallet.</p>\n\n\n  </article>\n\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n\n</details>",
